Name: DecTopNoCodePos
Desc: release top if not a CODEPOS

Name: Bit_Or
Desc: Pop a;b and push a | b

Name: Bit_Xor
Desc: Pop a;b and push a ^ b

Name: GetEmptyArray
Desc: Alloc array; push the (x01_POINTER)ref on the stack; addref to inst and release it

Name: GetString
Desc: Push (string)mt_stringref on the stack; create 2658987327 when too many

Name: Modulus
Desc: Pop 2 values and push the modulus

Name: VectorConstant
Desc: Allocate a vector and set flag values 0b00XXYYZZ VV: 00=0; 01=-1; 10=1

Name: SizeOf
Desc: Pop an element and push the size; error 3222417139 if not a string or an array

Name: Vector
Desc: Pop 3 elements; Alloc and push a vector from them

Name: DecTop
Desc: Pop and release a value of the stack

Name: GetVector
Desc: Push (vector)&x on the stack (use the asm value to describe it)
